- For XM2X period, [ENTITY 3] rented an advertising billboard at the xxxx airport for 6 months which attracted cost of approximately USD 0.2 million per month. However, Management informed us that this channel of advertising will not recur after [MONTH] 20X3. We, therefore, proposed to remove this as it’s deemed as a one-off item.
- [ENTITY 3] received a dividend from [ENTITY 1] of USD 0.4 million in [MONTH] 20X2, within XM2X period. According to Management, [ENTITY 3] had never received a dividend from [ENTITY 1] and no restriction of dividend payment is stated in the investment contract. However, we have not been informed of the reason for this dividend payment. We, therefore, proposed to remove this income as it was a non-operating item.
